dotfiles for osx

Currently using the following:

* terminal is Hyper `.hyper.js`
* Hyper theme is 'hyper-materialshell' (per config)
* shell is zsh with oh-my-zsh `.zshrc`
* oh-my-zsh theme is https://github.com/carloscuesta/materialshell
* npm packages are globally installed per `.npmrc`
* eslint config uses airbnb style guide
* vim colorscheme is hybrid_material (via plugin: kristijanhusak/vim-hybrid-material)
* OSX Terminal theme is https://github.com/carloscuesta/materialshell
* OSX Terminal is only used if Hyper is unavailable
